NETLI_MULTIROUTES_CHECKBOX.message: Enables the WebRTC multiple-routes option in Chrome's privacy settings.

NETLI_NONPROXIEDUDP_CHECKBOX.message: Enables UDP traffic. If unchecked, UDP traffic can be allowed only if a UDP supported proxy is configured.

NETLI_APPDESC.message: Configures how WebRTC's network traffic is routed by changing Chrome's privacy settings.
